data.description: COME SEE THIS COZY & COMFORTABLE BRICK HOME THAT IS MOVE IN READY! CHARMING INTERIOR W/ BEAUTIFUL REAL WOOD SHUTTERS FOR AN OLD FASHIONED FEEL & PRIVACY. AN EXPANSIVE KITCHEN W/ELECT RANGE, WARM HICKORY CABINETS & NEW, NICE BIG PANTRY! DUAL PANE WINDOWS IN MOST ROOMS. NEWER PROPANE FURNACE INSTALLED & WOOD STOVE W/ BLOWER FAN. SPLIT BEDROOMS W/ THE BONUS OF THE 4TH BEDROOM SET UP AS AN OFFICE. MATURE LILAC BUSHES & TREES W/ GREAT POTENTIAL FOR LANDSCAPING/GARDENING IN THE FULLY 6' CHAIN LINK FENCED YARD TO CREATE A BEAUTIFUL ENVIRONMENT. WIDE ENTRY GATE INTO NORTH SIDE OF FENCED BACK YARD W/ UTILITY SHED INCLUDED. WALK ONE BLOCK TO THE PARK W/ SPLASH POOL, WALK ONE BLOCK TO BASHAS, & ONLY 10 MINUTES FM NATIONAL FOREST! EASY MOUNTAIN LIVING!
